 these\neffects are generic over a wider range of supernova progenitors.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 16 Jun 2015 20:24:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 16 Jul 2015 04:14:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-07-17"}
