l that can estimate the correct exchange parameters and outline\nthe quantum phase diagrams, which can be useful for experimental fitting\nprocesses in frustrated quantum magnets.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 17 Jun 2015 05:41:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 10 Dec 2015 06:30:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-12-11"}
