om their mass and rotation period largely independent\nfrom the wind braking model adopted. These effectively represent\ngyro-chronology relationships that take into account the physics of the\ntwo-zone model for the stellar angular momentum evolution.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 17 Jun 2015 12:21:18 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 18 Sep 2015 18:25:38 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 12 Oct 2015 10:25:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-11-18"}
